'''白花丹素'''（'''Plumbagin'''，'''5-hydroxy-2-methyl-1,4-naphthoquinone'''）为[[萘醌|萘醌]][[衍生物|衍生物]]，为黄色染料。<ref name=walnut>[http://www.drugs.com/npp/black-walnut.html Black Walnut] {{Wayback|url=http://www.drugs.com/npp/black-walnut.html |date=20210418025027 }}. Drugs.com.</ref>其得名于植物[[白花丹|白花丹]]{{small|（''Plumbago''）}}。<ref>Van der Vijver, L.M. 1972. Distribution of plumbagin in the Plumbaginaceae. ''Phytochemistry'' '''11''': 3247–3248.</ref>白花丹素常见于[[茅膏菜|茅膏菜]]和[[猪笼草|猪笼草]]体内。<ref>Wang, W., X. Luo, & H. Li 2010. Terahertz and infrared spectra of plumbagin, juglone, and menadione. ''[[食虫植物通讯|Carnivorous Plant Newsletter]]'' '''39'''(3): 82–88.</ref>

== 药理性质 ==
各种细胞和动物模型试验中得出了以下药理学特性：
*[[抗菌剂|抗菌]]<ref>Didry, N., L. Dubrevil & M. Pinkas 1994. Activity of anthraquinonic and naphthoquinonic compounds on oral bacteria. ''Die Pharmazie'' '''49'''(9): 681–683.</ref><ref>Paiva, S.R.d., M.R. Figueiredo, T. V. Aragão, M.A.C. Kaplan 2003. {{PDFlink|[http://www.scielo.br/pdf/mioc/v98n7/v98n7a17.pdf Antimicrobial Activity in Vitro of Plumbagin Isolated from ''Plumbago'' Species.]|511 [[Kibibyte|KiB]]<!-- application/pdf, 523331 bytes -->}} ''Mem Inst Oswaldo Cruz'' '''98'''(7): 959–961.</ref>
*[[疟疾|抗疟疾]]<ref>Likhitwitayawuid, K., R. Kaewamatawong, N. Ruangrungsi & J. Krungkrai 1998. Antimalarial naphthoquinones from ''Nepenthes thorelii''. ''Planta Medica'' '''64'''(3): 237–241.</ref>
*[[炎症|抗炎]]<ref>Checker R., Sharma D., Sandur S.K., Subrahmanyam G., Krishnan S., Poduval T.B., Sainis K.B. "Plumbagin inhibits proliferative and inflammatory responses of T cells independent of ROS generation but by modulating intracellular thiols"  ''Journal of Cellular Biochemistry'' 2010 110:5 (1082-1093)</ref>
*[[癌症|抗癌]]<ref>Parimala, R. & P. Sachdanandam 1993. Effect of plumbagin on some glucose metabolizing enzymes studied in rats in experimental hepatoma. ''Molecular and Cellular Biochemistry'' '''12'''(1): 59–63.</ref><ref>Hsu, Y.-L., C.-Y. Cho, P.-L. Kuo, Y.-T. Huang & C.-C. Lin 2006. Plumbagin (5-Hydroxy-2-methyl-1,4-naphthoquinone) Induces Apoptosis and Cell Cycle Arrest in A549 Cells through p53 Accumulation via c-Jun NH2-Terminal Kinase-Mediated Phosphorylation at Serine 15 in Vitro and in Vivo. ''Journal of Pharmacology and Experimental Therapeutics'' '''318'''(2): 484–494. {{DOI|10.1124/jpet.105.098863}} PMID 16632641</ref>
*[[强心剂|强心]]<ref>Itoigawa, M., K. Takeya & H. Furukawa 1991. Cardiotonic action of plumbagin on guinea-pig papillary muscle. ''Planta Medica'' '''57'''(4): 317–319.</ref>
*[[免疫抑制剂|免疫抑制]]<ref>McKallip, Robert J. Lombard, Catherine. Sun, Jingping. Ramakrishnan, Rupal.	"Plumbagin-induced apoptosis in lymphocytes is mediated through increased reactive oxygen species production, upregulation of Fas, and activation of the caspase cascade."''Toxicology & Applied Pharmacology''. 247(1):41-52, 2010 Aug 15.</ref>
*[[避孕药|抗生育]]<ref>Bhargava, S.K. 1984. Effects of plumbagin on reproductive function of male dog. ''Indian Journal of Experimental Biology'' '''22'''(3): 153–156.</ref>
*神经保护<ref>Son TG. Camandola S. Arumugam TV. Cutler RG. Telljohann RS. Mughal MR. Moore TA. Luo W. Yu QS. Johnson DA. Johnson JA. Greig NH. Mattson MP.	Plumbagin, a novel Nrf2/ARE activator, protects against cerebral ischemia.</ref>
*[[动脉粥样硬化|抗动脉粥样硬化]]<ref>Ding, Y., Z.-J. Chen, S. Liu, D. Che, M. Vetter, C.-H. Chang 2005. Inhibition of Nox-4 activity by plumbagin, a plant-derived bioactive naphthoquinone. ''Journal of Pharmacy and Pharmacology'' '''57'''(1): 111.</ref>

